        "body": "<p>Use <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>LocalBluetoothDevice localBT = LocalBluetoothDevice.initLocalDevice(this);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>or<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Context context = this;\nLocalBluetoothDevice localBT = LocalBluetoothDevice.initLocalDevice(context);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
